      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/ftc-calls-microsoft-s-game-pass-price-increase-anti-competitive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国联邦贸易委员会在一份上诉法庭文件中对微软公司视频游戏订阅服务价格上涨表示担忧。]]></description>
